{"tid":2452710,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"rubberBand ciao 6號加場歡呼區","createTime":"2021-03-19T04:09:30.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-19T04:31:42.000Z","uid":343629,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"3374aec6fb1744ef9c386e010f4525cc0a0462f6","tid":2452710,"uid":343629,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-19T04:09:30.000Z","msg":"RubberBand正式宣佈加開第二場<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n好興奮呀我買嘅頭場 ，咁多位前幾日買嘅尾場全部都係假㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但恭喜恭喜加開多一場<br />\n<br />\n兄弟朋友紅館見<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/nope.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/nope.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n&mdash;&mdash;-<br />\n之前實在太多朋友話買唔到飛，經過主辦單位嘅同事兩日嚟頻頻撲撲同埋大家嘅大力集氣，我哋正式宣布，加開4月6日一場!!!!!<br />\n<br />\n真係最後加場喇，門票將於3月25日（下星期四）早上10時正式開售。<br />\n<br />\n暐嗱嗱，知你哋想問乜㗎吓係咪想問點解加場25號先賣飛？今次堅係臨急臨忙話加就加噪，俾啲時間我哋，幫緊你幫緊你。<br />\n<br />\n6號，加6號吖唔該！＃6號加6號＃加場定加長<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/p/CMlcw3ig12I/?igshid=ey24qw8zv9qy\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FCMlcw3ig12I%2F%3Figshid%3Dey24qw8zv9qy&d=Ip59BN4yZo1XWf66eFhBSpgFNMRZLCTiZeA0y1vO9n4%3D&h=6ba2a26a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FCMlcw3ig12I%2F%3Figshid%3Dey24qw8zv9qy&h=b8c1109e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/p/CMlcw3ig12I/?igshid=ey24qw8zv9qy</a><br />\n<br />\nRubberBand嘅咁多位如果你睇到我想同你講我愛你<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n仲有<strong><span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\">光復香港時代革命<br />\n</span></span></strong><br />\n<span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\"><strong>五大訴求決一不可</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"5744b9cf8c2f3f1a7ecf03